Cloneable, GeoCodeExtension, LayerExtension
public final class GeoCodeExtension
extends BaseGeoCodeExtension

this is the implementation of GeoCoding for a Layer that originates from the ArcIMS server.

Example of usage:

      static {
         _extensionRegistry = new com.esri.mo2.map.ext.Registry();
           // add standard extensions here
           _extensionRegistry.put(FeatureClassProxyImpl.GeoCodeExtension.GEOCODE, FeatureClassProxyImpl.GeoCodeExtension.class);
           _extensionRegistry.put(FeatureClassProxyImpl.StoredQueryExtension.STOREDQUERY, FeatureClassProxyImpl.StoredQueryExtension.class);
       }
